    "The Table 6 illustrates the citation profile of core authors in the field from 2001 to 2024 and enables identification of their strengths and years of impact.",
    "Among the earlier contributors, Muller S (2003) and Pena R (2004) were updating mid2000s, while Pena impact was till 2011, which is an indication that he made some of the foundational work in the field of DFIG or related technology.",
    "Leonhard W and Brekken Tka has also significant contribution but they active only in late 2000s.",
    "If we go to the recent years, the highest citation strength is observed in Xiong L, 2019 with 37.12 and a rising trend from 2021 to 2024 because of recent innovation in the field.",
